fields.description:
{html}

Expected: iPhone apps built against SDK 3.2 will launch in iPad emulator centered at iPhone screen size.

Observed: iPad emulator launches with centered all black iPhone screen. Error Failed to load NSMainNibFile MainWindow_ipad' appears in logs.

Steps to reproduce:

  1. Click New Project
  2. Select type 'mobile'
  3. Complete form
  4. Click Test & Package tab
  5. Select SDK 3.2 in iPhone tab
